To run c programs do:
```
    cd c_code
    gcc filename.c -o filename -flags
    ./filename.exe
```

`-fno-stack-protector -Wall`

To run rust do:
```
    cargo new project_name
    cargo run
```
to run main.rs.

Otherwise do 
```
    cargo run --bin filename
```

(cargo new projectname creates a new folder with src and everything)
(Each rust file )